group bundletrans(source src : questionnaireResponse, target bundle : Bundle) {
  src -> bundle.id = uuid() "id";
  src -> bundle.type = 'batch' "type";
  src where src.item.where(linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE01').exists() then {
    src ->  bundle.entry as entry,  entry.request as request,  request.method = 'POST',  entry.resource = create('Observation') as tgt then emcareobservationemcareb22de01(src, tgt) "DE01";
  } "emcareobservation";
  src where src.item.where(linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE02').exists() then {
    src ->  bundle.entry as entry,  entry.request as request,  request.method = 'POST',  entry.resource = create('Observation') as tgt then emcareobservationemcareb22de02(src, tgt) "DE02";
  } "emcareobservation";

    src ->  bundle.entry as entry,  entry.request as request,  request.method = 'POST',  entry.resource = create('Observation') as tgt then emcareobservationemcareb22de03(src, tgt) "DE03";
  } "emcareobservation";
  src where src.item.where(linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE04').exists() then {
    src ->  bundle.entry as entry,  entry.request as request,  request.method = 'POST',  entry.resource = create('Observation') as tgt then emcareobservationemcareb22de04(src, tgt) "DE04";
  } "emcareobservation";
  src where src.item.where(linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE05').exists() then {
    src ->  bundle.entry as entry,  entry.request as request,  request.method = 'POST',  entry.resource = create('Observation') as tgt then emcareobservationemcareb22de05(src, tgt) "DE05";
  } "emcareobservation";
  src where src.item.where(linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE07').exists() then {
    src ->  bundle.entry as entry,  entry.request as request,  request.method = 'POST',  entry.resource = create('Observation') as tgt then emcareobservationemcareb22de07(src, tgt) "DE07";
  } "emcareobservation";
}

group emcareobservationemcareb22de01(source src, target tgt) {
  src ->  tgt.identifier = create('Identifier') as CodeID,  CodeID.system = 'http://hl7.org/fhir/namingsystem-identifier-type',  CodeID.use = 'official',  CodeID.value = 'uuid',  CodeID.id = uuid() "id-emcareb22de01";
  src.encounter as encounter -> tgt.encounter = encounter "35bc6b82";
  src.subject as subject ->  tgt.subject = subject,  tgt.meta = create('Meta') as newMeta,  newMeta.profile = 'https://fhir.dk.swisstph-mis.ch/matchbox/fhir/StructureDefinition/emcareobservation',  tgt.code = create('CodeableConcept') as concept,  concept.coding = create('Coding') as coding,  coding.system = 'https://fhir.dk.swisstph-mis.ch/matchbox/fhir/CodeSystem/emcare-custom-codes',  coding.code = 'EmCare.B22.DE01' "code-emcareb22de01";
  src.item as item where linkId = 'timestamp' then {
    item.answer first as a then {
      a.value as val -> tgt.issued = val "8945c96b";
    } "4272fc8b";
  } "f4472f32";
  src.subject as subject -> tgt.subject = subject "patient";
  src.item first as item where linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE01' then {
    item.answer first as a then {
      a.value as val ->  tgt.value = val,  tgt.status = 'final' "val-emcareb22de01";
    } "an-emcareb22de01";
  } "it-emcareb22de01";
}
